      "text": "Many Statements",
      "level": "h2"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "Most C programs contain many statements.",
      "html": "<p>Most C programs contain many statements.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "metadata": {},
      "text": "The statements are executed, one by one, in the same order as they are written:",
      "html": "<p>The statements are executed, one by one, in the same order as they are \nwritten:</p>"
